<br>
Personally, I enjoy this new crowd control role. It really makes me feel like I can contribute something important and new to the groups I play with. If there is some type of bug affecting its utility I hope verant looks at it and fixes it. I'd hate to have to go back to being afraid to send my pet at a mob who was beating on a chanter because of concern that the pet would break the chanter's mez should the chanter succeed in landing one. <p><html>
