<br>
With the recent changes you can now issue multiple commands with no delay, so my pet hold key looks like this:<br>
<br>
/pet hold<br>
/pet back off<br>
<br>
<br>
Pet stops attack, and report calming down message.<br>
<br>
Hate list wiped and pet is on hold at the<br>
<br>
/guard here <br>
<br>
location works great.<br>
